				<td colspan="2"><span>Yes, there are two new epic weapons 1.5 and 2.0. It is not required that you have obtained epic 1.0 but if you haven't you will have to complete more steps (as you have not 'proven' yourself yet).
<br />

<br />
It seems from data obtained through Lucy that each class weapon has a combination of two effects that are either focus, click, or proc. The effects are similar for both weapons with 2.0 giving greater benfit. I'm under the impression that for the time being epic 2.0 will only be accessable by the highest lvl players in the strongest guilds as the encounters will be extremely difficult.
<br />

<br />
